feat(research): Research Infrastructure Phase complete

Phase 1 — TOP100 Universe
- backend/app/universe/{curated,liquidity_filter,sector_classifier,
  universe_builder,manager}.py
- Curated ~90 symbol universe across 16+ sectors (TWSE-50, mid-cap
  leaders, TPEX growth, 5 major ETFs)
- UniverseSnapshot model + alembic 0005
- Weekly liquidity filter (>= NT$50M notional/day)
- UniverseManager: get_active_universe, get_sector_members,
  get_liquid_symbols, sector_breakdown

Phase 2 — Edge schema extension
- EdgeSignal: sector, mfe_r, mae_r columns
- StrategyPerformanceDaily table (daily snapshot for ranker history)
- alembic 0005_research_infra (batch ALTER + new tables)

Phase 3 — Real Performance Tracking
- signal_evaluator: writes MFE / MAE alongside outcomes (intrabar
  excursion, lookahead-free)
- app/edge/strategy_metrics.py: overall / by_setup / by_regime /
  by_sector / setup_x_regime — reads ONLY from evaluated edge_signals
- app/edge/edge_decay.py: recent (30d) vs older (60-90d) expectancy
  comparison, labels {improving, stable, decaying, broken}
- app/edge/performance_monitor.py: one-shot snapshot payload

Phase 4 — Narrative Intelligence
- app/narrative/theme_tracker.py: deterministic keyword scoring across
  12 known themes (AI 半導體, CoWoS, 航運, ETF, 法說會, ...)
- app/narrative/capital_flow_detector.py: institutional focus from
  volume anomalies × chip streaks
- app/narrative/narrative_engine.py: market_style classifier
  (risk_on / risk_off / neutral / mixed), dominant_themes,
  leading_sector, institutional_focus, risk_factors, market_summary

Phase 5 — Strategy Ranking System
- app/strategy_registry/ranker.py: composite rank
  = 0.30 * normalize(oos_sharpe)
  + 0.25 * normalize(profit_factor - 1)
  + 0.20 * sigmoid(live_expectancy_R)
  + 0.15 * (1 - max(0, -decay))
  + 0.10 * normalize(mc_p05_ratio)
- Production gate: ACTIVE / WATCH / DISABLED / UNKNOWN
- Disabled when sample<30 | live_pf<1.2 | live_exp<0 | consec_loss>8

Phase 7 — Adaptive Scanner
- scanner returns adaptive_score per row:
    live_expectancy_R * regime_confidence * strategy_rank * chip_strength
- Disabled-by-ranker setups excluded by default
- Each row carries production_status + adaptive_breakdown

Phase 8 — Research Automation
- Scheduler additions (Asia/Taipei):
  16:00 evaluate_signals (walk-forward outcome marking)
  17:00 strategy_ranking_refresh (writes StrategyPerformanceDaily)
  18:00 daily_report (warms research markdown cache)
  Sun 23:00 universe_rebuild (weekly snapshot)
- app/services/research_report.py: markdown rendering of full daily
  research report

Phase 9 — Production Gates formalized in ranker.GATE

Phase 10 — Terminal Upgrade
- New /terminal panels: MARKET NARRATIVE (style + themes + risk factors
  + institutional focus), STRATEGY HEALTH (live rank table)
- New /terminal/performance subpage with Live Edge tables:
  OVERALL stats, STRATEGY RANK with production_status badges,
  BY SETUP / REGIME / SECTOR breakdowns, SETUP × REGIME matrix,
  EDGE DECAY table with labels

New APIs
- /api/v1/performance/{snapshot, by-setup, by-regime, by-sector,
  setup-x-regime, decay}
- /api/v1/narrative/today
- /api/v1/universe/{active, sectors, rebuild}
- /api/v1/strategy-rank/
- /api/v1/research/{today, today.md}

Iron rules upheld
- No lookahead — evaluator walks forward only
- All data traceable — edge_signals real outcomes only for performance
- No fake stats — backtest data never mixed into performance APIs
- Production gates enforced in scanner & ranker
- TOP100 universe deterministic, hand-curated, version-controlled

Tests: 117/117 passing
- test_research_infra.py (10 new):
  * universe build/manager + curated uniqueness
  * MFE/MAE evaluator
  * by-setup / by-regime breakdowns
  * theme tracker positive + negative
  * ranker no-data + low-sample
  * decay labels

Frontend build: 22 routes, 0 errors

